{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't communicate because I didn't speak Polish, and I didn't speak German or Dutch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I remember every period of time, we had to change shifts from day shift to night shift.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the factory supplied during the work shift a period where they could, you know, take a break, where they had their lunch.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- they had a kitchen there that prepared one particular food like mixed potatoes with vegetables and sometimes a piece of ham or so on there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was free for the workers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Luckily, the women that are with me didn't like that food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They always brought their own sandwiches along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But what they did when they worked night shift-- and this was dangerous-- when they went to get their food, they'd make believe they ate it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they hid it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They made sure that we saw where they hid it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then when the opportunity came, we were able to go there and gobble it down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, this was only possible during the night shift.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "During the weeks that we had the day shift, it was too dangerous because there were too many more people there watching.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was a-- a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Looking back, I think if I wouldn't have had this extra food that we got when we had the night shift, possibly I would have been reduced to the stage of what we called a Muselmann much earlier.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then we did have selections in Gleiwitz every period of time to make sure that we were still able to produce.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And sometimes we had to jump to make sure that we were able to jump far enough.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
